{"id":423657,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/01/前有高洁-后有雷克-顺之者昌-逆之者亡/","date":"2016-01-02T11:34:33Z","modified":"2016-02-11T22:36:48Z","title":"【立此存照】前有高洁 后有雷克，顺之者昌 逆之者亡","content":"<p>先回顾一下《环球时报》一周前<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/12/%E3%80%8A%E6%96%B0%E8%A7%82%E5%AF%9F%E5%AE%B6%E3%80%8B%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%97%A2%E5%BE%88%E5%81%8F%E6%BF%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%88%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A/\" target=\"_blank\">质疑法国媒体专业性</a>时的言论：</p>\n<blockquote><p>如果确实有人在Facebook上对高洁进行超出批评正常限度的围攻，我们反对。但Facebook不是中国网站，《新观察家》应该去找美国人扎克伯格交涉。如果高洁的确遭到应予重视的“死亡威胁”，那么我们强烈建议她报警。</p></blockquote>\n<p><em>（据无国界记者组织<a href=\"http://www.voachinese.com/content/voa-news-reporters-without-borders-20151201/3083053.html\" target=\"_blank\">声明</a>，针对高洁的死亡威胁出现在人民网评论版块，其照片住址等个人信息遭人肉后被公布在一些大陆门户网站论坛内。）</em></p>\n<p>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;-我是“众怒”的分割线&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;-</p>\n<p>中青网今日<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/01/423689/\" target=\"_blank\">发表评论称</a>德国人雷克“亵渎毛泽东惹众怒”，引来“网民齐呼驱逐”：</p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/5iyouth\" target=\"_blank\">@中国青年网</a>：【德国人雷克亵渎毛泽东惹众怒 网民齐呼驱逐】毛泽东是中华民族的符号，是精神信仰、民族脊梁。在美国歪曲攻击华盛顿，在英国辱骂女皇，雷克敢吗？ 我们不需要雷克任何虚情假意的道歉。国家应建立永久性的黑名单，把危害主流意识形态安全的洋流氓永远拒之门外，不得踏入一步！<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/a3d444e3gw1ezjzeqlpioj20kw0dbq48.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423685\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/a3d444e3gw1ezjzeqlpioj20kw0dbq48.jpg\" alt=\"a3d444e3gw1ezjzeqlpioj20kw0dbq48\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" /></a></p></blockquote>\n<p>中青网打马赛克的地方，是“畜生”二字：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-25.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423682\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-25.png\" alt=\"众怒-25\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>虽然在新浪微博的<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/01/423689/\" target=\"_blank\">并没有看到所谓的“众怒”</a></strong>，但中青网截图中的凤凰网<a href=\"http://comment.ifeng.com/view.php?docUrl=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ifeng.com%2Fa%2F20151231%2F46903695_0.shtml&amp;docName=%E4%B8%93%E5%AE%B6%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%B7%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%B7%E5%85%8B%E5%B0%86%E6%AF%9B%E6%B3%BD%E4%B8%9C%E6%AF%94%E4%BD%9C%E5%B8%8C%E7%89%B9%E5%8B%92%E8%BF%9D%E6%B3%95&amp;skey=0512d4\" target=\"_blank\">评论页</a>内，着实有相当一部分“众怒”言论<strong>其实是死亡威胁</strong>。这种现象当然<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/07/%E3%80%90%E5%9B%BE%E8%AF%B4%E5%A4%A9%E6%9C%9D%E3%80%91%E8%87%AA%E5%B9%B2%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%AC%E7%9A%84%E6%84%A4%E6%80%92/\" target=\"_blank\">并不罕见</a>，自干五们的“愤怒”一直都与人身威胁形影相随。</p>\n<p>以下评论截取自凤凰网《专家：雷克主观恶意评价毛泽东构成违法》一文的<a href=\"http://comment.ifeng.com/view.php?docUrl=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ifeng.com%2Fa%2F20151231%2F46903695_0.shtml&amp;docName=%E4%B8%93%E5%AE%B6%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%B7%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%B7%E5%85%8B%E5%B0%86%E6%AF%9B%E6%B3%BD%E4%B8%9C%E6%AF%94%E4%BD%9C%E5%B8%8C%E7%89%B9%E5%8B%92%E8%BF%9D%E6%B3%95&amp;skey=0512d4\">评论页</a>：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-02.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423659\"><img  src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-02.png\" alt=\"众怒-02\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-03.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423660\"><img  src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-03.png\" alt=\"众怒-03\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-04.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423661\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-04.png\" alt=\"众怒-04\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-05.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423662\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-05.png\" alt=\"众怒-05\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-06.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423663\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-06.png\" alt=\"众怒-06\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-07.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423664\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-07.png\" alt=\"众怒-07\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-08.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423665\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-08.png\" alt=\"众怒-08\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-09.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423666\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-09.png\" alt=\"众怒-09\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-10.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423667\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-10.png\" alt=\"众怒-10\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-11.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423668\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-11.png\" alt=\"众怒-11\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-12.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423669\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-12.png\" alt=\"众怒-12\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-13.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423670\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-13.png\" alt=\"众怒-13\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/f