g\" alt=\"众怒-22\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-23.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423680\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-23.png\" alt=\"众怒-23\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-24.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423681\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/众怒-24.png\" alt=\"众怒-24\" width=\"500\" height=\"\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>前有高洁，后有雷克。顺之者昌，逆之者亡。</strong></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,17016],"tags":[16016,20773,22609,20440,9375,9966,9091,8646,25859,23165,29750]}